<ion-header>
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>
      User Profile
    </ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content>
  <app-profile></app-profile>
  <ion-button expand="full" (click)="checkCart()">Check</ion-button>

  
  <ion-card-content *ngFor="let crew of cartCrews; let i = index">
    {{ crew.id }}
  </ion-card-content>
  
</ion-content>
